    "designScenario": {
      "description": "The Rain Protection System is engineered to prevent rainwater from obstructing the pilot's vision by employing advanced hydrophobic coatings and wiper systems on aircraft windshields. It integrates with the cockpit's control systems, enabling automatic and manual control modes. The system ensures visibility during adverse weather conditions, preserving safety and operational efficiency.",
